<div class="head">
    <p class="open1">Welcome to Movies Management System</p>
    <p class="open2">Our platform is designed to help you easily manage your favorite movies.</p>
    <p class="open2">Whether you're a film enthusiast, a casual viewer, or just looking for some entertainment, our system has something for everyone.</p>
    <p class="intro">Our System has integrated the CRUD (Create, Read, Update, and Delete) functions and more, which means everything is under your control!</p>
    <ul class="crudList">
        <li>
            <p><strong>Create:</strong> The "Create" function allows you to add new movies to the system. This can be done by filling out a form with information such as the movie title, director, publication year, genre, and ratings. Once the information is submitted, the movie will be added to the system and will be available for other users to browse.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Read:</strong> The "Read" function allows you to view the details of movies that are already in the system. You can view details such as the movie title, director, publication year, genre, ratings, and who has associated with.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Update: </strong> The "Update" function allows you to edit or update the information of a movie that is already in the system. You can modify information such as the movie title, director, publication year, genre, and ratings. And you can also upload a related poster image for the movie. The updated information will be saved in the system and will be available to other users.  </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Delete: </strong> The "Delete" function allows you to remove a movie from the system. There will be a confirmation when you attempt to delete the movie. Once the movie is deleted, it will no longer be available in the system, and other users would not get access to it.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Upload picture:</strong> The "Upload picture" feature allows you to select and transfer an image file from your local computer to the system. You can browse the movie details page and upload a poster image for the movie. The uploaded picture will be stored in the system and will be available to other users.
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

